  &lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;Big Data Oriented Foudation of Tsinghua National Laboratory for Information Science and Technology, Internet Information Platform Driven by Big Data &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;National Natural Science Fundation for Excellent Young Scholar of China (No. 61222213): Architecture of Computer Networks (2013-2015) &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;National Natural Science Foundation of China (No.61170290): Theory Research on Server Placement of large-scale overlay networks (2012-2015); &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;National Basic Research Program of China (The 973 Programs, No. 2012CB315800): Research on Architecture and Mechanism of Service-Oriented Future Internet (2012-2016); &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; National Basic Research Program of China (The 973 Programs, No. 2011CB302601): Fundamental Research on High Performance and Trustworthy Virtual Computing Environment (2011-2015); &lt;/li&gt;
