    &lt;li&gt; National Basic Research Program of China (The 973 Programs, No. 2011CB302601): Fundamental Research on High Performance and Trustworthy Virtual Computing Environment (2011-2015); &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;International Cooperation and Exchange of National Natural Science Foundation of China (No.60736012): Green Network- Theory and Technology of Reducing Energy Consumption of Network (2011-2014); &lt;/li&gt;
